msgstr "现在用 §0 验证等式。"

#: Game.Levels.Analysis.L02_SumLimit
msgid "If `u` tends to `l` and `v` tends `l'` then `u+v` tends to `l+l'`.\n"
"You will need to use `rcases` to extract `N` from the limit definitions."
msgstr "如果 `u` 趋向于 `l` 且 `v` 趋向于 `l'`，那么 `u+v` 趋向于 `l+l'`。\n"
"你需要使用 `rcases` 从极限定义中提取 `N`。"

