#. §1: `hn`
#: Game.Levels.Analysis.L01_SequenceLimit
msgid "Now introduce §0 and §1."
msgstr "现在引入 §0 和 §1。"

#: Game.Levels.Algebra
msgid "Algebra"
msgstr "代数"

#: Game.Levels.Logic.L05_Forall
msgid "Universal quantifiers allow us to state properties that hold for all elements of a type."
msgstr "全称量词允许我们陈述对类型的所有元素都成立的属性。"

#: Game.Levels.Logic.L04_Equivalences
msgid "Equivalences"
msgstr "等价"

#: Game.Levels.Logic.L06_Exists
msgid "Existential quantifiers assert the existence of an element satisfying a property."
msgstr "存在量词断言满足某种属性的元素的存在。"
